*Pismo* je stiglo od prijatelja iz Kanade. (The letter has arrived from a friend in Canada.)

Moj brat je napisao *pismo* mojoj majci. (My brother wrote a letter to my mother.)

Poslednje *pismo* je bilo tužno. (The last letter was sad.)

Ona je čitala *pismo* u sobi. (She was reading the letter in the room.)

*Pisma* su bila dostavljena na vreme. (The letters were delivered on time.)